trans-unit.source: Provides a managed equivalent of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_DBinding" name="DBinding" href=""></xref> interface from the Microsoft Data Binding Collection library (msbind) for use in applications upgraded from Visual Basic 6.0.
trans-unit.target: Gir et administrert som tilsvarer det <xref uid="langword_csharp_DBinding" name="DBinding" href=""> </xref> grensesnittet fra Microsofts Binding innsamling-biblioteket (msbind) for bruk i programmer som er oppgradert fra Visual Basic 6.0.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating that data has changed.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir at dataene er endret.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if data has changed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis dataene er endret. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_String" name="String" href=""></xref> that contains the data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_String" name="String" href=""> </xref> som inneholder dataene.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the data format for a data field.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir datatypen for et datafelt.

trans-unit.source: Gets the key value for a data field.
A <xref uid="langword_csharp_String" name="String" href=""></xref> that contains the key value.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_String" name="String" href=""> </xref> som inneholder nøkkelverdien.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of a property from a data object.
trans-unit.target: Henter navnet på en egenskap av et dataobjekt.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_String" name="String" href=""></xref> that contains the property name.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_String" name="String" href=""> </xref> som inneholder navnet på egenskapen.
